ing The Courier-Journal in southern Indiana flooded me like a drenching sho=
wer. What a fantastic framing of your
question. I always feel like I=E2=80=99m in your room while listening to yo=
ur pods.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94A happy Puck subscriber

More on the =E2=80=98Varsity=E2=80=99 podcast: =E2=80=9CIs Marchand gonna b=
e a guest soon, or does the abuse just continue indefinitely (which is fine=
)?=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94Another happy Puck subscriber

